	</div>
				<h1 id="headline" class="eza-title">
											
Parties over? Republicans, Democrats, and the Howard Schultz challenge									</h1>
			</div>
		</div>

		
				<div class="row">
			<div class="editor-intro small-centered eza-body small-12 medium-11">
				<h2 class="title text-center">Why We Wrote This</h2>
				<div>
					
<p>Weaker political parties along with more extreme partisanship have made for a dangerous combination – one that experts say threatens democratic norms. This is the sixth installment of our&nbsp;<a href="https://www.csmonitor.com/USA/Topics/Democracy-Under-Strain" target="_blank" rel="noopener">“Democracy Under Strain” series.</a></p>				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
				<article id="story-content">
			
